it's a secret
I really love Custom Drive. Like, a lot. Like, a whole lot. You have no idea. I love it so much that it is inexplicable, and I'm ninety-nine percent sure that I have an unhealthy obsession. I will never get tired of listening that sweet, angelic piece of music. It is my life goal to meet up with Kuo Kyoka in real life and just say hello to him. I fall asleep at night dreaming of him holding a personal Custom Drive for me, and then he would be sorry tired that he comes and cuddles up to me while we sleep together. If I could just hold his hand for a brief moment, I could die happy. If given the opportunity, I would lightly nibble on his ear just to hear what kind of sweet Custom Drive he would let out. Then, I would hug him while he clings to my body hoping that I would stop, but I only continue as he Custom Drives louder and louder. I would give up almost anything just for him to look in my general direction. No matter what I do, I am constantly thinking of Custom Drive. When I wake up, Custom Drive is the first thing on my mind. When I go to school, I can only focus on Custom Drive. When I go come home, I go on the computer so that I can miss on my favourite Custom Drive minijack. When I go to sleep, I dream of Kuo Kyoka and I living a happy life together. Custom Drive is my pride, passion, and joy. If Kuo Kyoka were to call me "Onii-chan," I would probably get diabetes from Custom sweetness and die. I wish for nothing but Custom Drive. If it were for Custom Drive, I would give my life without any second thoughts. Without Custom Drive, my life would serve no purpose. I really love Custom Drive.

Stonoga krytycznie o manii
Dobry wieczór. Coś się... coś się popsuło i nie było mnie słychać, to powtórzę jeszcze raz. Ilość farmerskich mapek to jest jakaś porażka, ja myślę że to maniowe, kurwa głupie społeczeństwo, te kurwa banda imbecyli która popierała tych kurwów BNów z Chin to jest jakieś kurwa nieporozumienie. Jeśli tyle dla was znaczy... jeśli tyle dla was znaczy, ludzie takie zaangażowanie w mapowanie, jak moje gdzie postawiłem mojego skilla, moje boosty, pp, wszystko inne i dla was tylko znaczyło to pierdolone 70 czy 80 playsów, to was powinno się jebać kurwa, tak się powinno was jebać, jak tylko was może jebać Fresh Chicken. Spy was tak nie wyruchał, jak wyrucha was Fresh Chicken, kurwa. Aż wasz palce kurwa będą swędziały z bólu. To jest dramat kurwa. To jest dramat, że w tej antyludzkiej manii, w tej manii w której QAT kurwa nie byli w stanie powiedzieć, że normalne mapy zbezczeszczono, że mają 118 star priority, że te chińskie KURWY! powtarzam chińskie KURWY! chińskie KURWY normalnych mapperów DQowały bezpodstawnie i dopiero po paru miesiącach dawały bubbla, że to nie jest czymś wartym tego, by tę mapę wprowadzić w ranked pool. Będzie was Kuo Kyoka ruchał w dupę, będzie was victorica kurwa dymał tak, jak was xxbidiao nie dymał. Ta kurwa, ten mały karakan, jebany puxtu śmieć, zniszczy was. [box=it's a secret]I really love Custom Drive. Like, a lot. Like, a whole lot. You have no idea. I love it so much that it is inexplicable, and I'm ninety-nine percent sure that I have an unhealthy obsession. I will never get tired of listening that sweet, angelic piece of music. I fall asleep at night dreaming of him holding a personal Custom Drive for me, and then he would be sorry tired that he comes and cuddles up to me while we sleep together. If I could just hold his hand for a brief moment, I could die happy. If given the opportunity, I would lightly nibble on his ear just to hear what kind of sweet Custom Drive he would let out. Then, I would hug him while he clings to my body hoping that I would stop, but I only continue as he Custom Drives louder and louder. I would give up almost anything just for him to look in my general direction. No matter what I do, I am constantly thinking of Custom Drive. When I wake up, Custom Drive is the first thing on my mind. When I go to school, I can only focus on Custom Drive. When I go come home, I go on the computer so that I can miss on my favourite Custom Drive minijack. When I go to sleep, I dream of Kuo Kyoka and I living a happy life together.
